kahaani is a 2012 indian thriller film written and directed by sujoy . the film features vidya balan , arjun rampal and arjun rampal in the lead roles . music of the film has been composed by ashok bhadra . the film is a sequel to the 2012 film of the same name . the film stars vidya balan and arjun rampal in the lead roles . music of the film has been composed by ashok bhadra .